flowchart LR
    E[Event consumed] --> H{Handler success?}
    H -->|Yes| OK[Commit offset]
    H -->|No| R[Schedule retry]
    R --> A{attempt >= max?}
    A -->|No| B[Exponential backoff]
    B --> W[Wait next_retry_at]
    W --> E
    A -->|Yes| D[Insert DLQ record]
    D --> K[ship-orders-dlq topic]
    D --> PG[(PostgreSQL dead_letter_messages)]

